## EmbeddableFactory.canCreateNew() method

If false, this type of embeddable can't be created with the "createNew" functionality. Instead, use createFromSavedObject, where an existing saved object must first exist.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
canCreateNew(): boolean;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`boolean`
